These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, march
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, aristoff
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, engineer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, sports
City: london, boston
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, taxi
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Birthday      | march     | february |
| Cigar         | aristoff  | cain       |
| Job           | engineer   | accountant    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | documentary   |
| City   | boston      | london     |
| Sport         | volleyball | swimming      |
| Transport     | taxi       | bus           |

