.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
2 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, police-officer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, sailing
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, purple
2 different pets are kept: cat, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, van
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the manager##1
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | sprite         | cola       |
| Game          | snooker        | mah-jongg |
| Job           | police-officer | manager    |
| Sport   | sailing        | handball  |
| Color   | purple        | lavender       |
| Pet           | rat            | cat        |
| Transport     | van            | ship       |

