.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, video-games
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, argentine
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, zombie
2 different pets are kept: hamster, horse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, prince
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, metal
1. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
5. the argentine is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | water       | coffee     |
| Hobby         | video-games | reading    |
| Nationality           | argentine   | turkish |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | zombie     |
| Pet           | hamster     | horse      |
| Cigar         | old-henry     | prince     |
| Music-Genre     | metal  | gospel        |

