2 different pets are kept: lizard, rat
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, watermelon
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the russian##1
2. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking fanta is the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the british is the person eating watermelon##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
6. the fisherman is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Job           | journalist    | fisherman  |
| Movie-Genre   | romance       | mystery    |
| Hobby   | board-games        | rock-climbing       |
| Nationality   | russian       | british    |
| Pet           | rat           | lizard     |
| Food         | blueberry | watermelon |
| Beverage     | tea    | fanta        |

